WEBVTT

00:00:00.120 --> 00:00:02.400
everyday hundreds of thousands of

00:00:02.400 --> 00:00:05.460
people pass through Hammad International Airport

00:00:05.960 --> 00:00:08.540
different fases different names

00:00:08.640 --> 00:00:10.020
different stories

00:00:10.760 --> 00:00:14.300
but every single one of them has to stop at the same place

00:00:14.520 --> 00:00:16.540
and answer the same question

00:00:19.520 --> 00:00:22.060
officers watch scanners run

00:00:22.200 --> 00:00:24.620
passports get checked one by one

00:00:25.080 --> 00:00:27.700
most people pass without a second glance

00:00:28.160 --> 00:00:31.020
but today somewhere in this crowd

00:00:31.160 --> 00:00:33.440
two people are moving through these gates

00:00:33.440 --> 00:00:34.940
with something to hide

00:00:35.520 --> 00:00:38.780
and two young interns have been given one job

00:00:39.360 --> 00:00:41.840
find them before they disappear

00:00:41.840 --> 00:00:44.540
their supervisor keeps it simple

00:00:44.640 --> 00:00:46.980
two photos two faces

00:00:47.200 --> 00:00:49.340
a man black hair

00:00:49.520 --> 00:00:51.820
gray eyes no beard

00:00:52.080 --> 00:00:53.560
a woman brown

00:00:53.560 --> 00:00:57.580
curly hair classes a full around their face

00:00:58.080 --> 00:01:00.000
their passports will be clean

00:01:00.000 --> 00:01:01.940
their stories will hold up

00:01:02.160 --> 00:01:05.060
the computer will clear them without station

00:01:05.280 --> 00:01:07.240
the interns are the last line

00:01:07.240 --> 00:01:09.180
catch them or they walk

00:01:09.760 --> 00:01:11.940
a man steps up to the desk

00:01:12.040 --> 00:01:14.040
brown hair full beard

00:01:14.040 --> 00:01:17.140
warm brown eyes relaxed smile

00:01:17.160 --> 00:01:19.160
he slides his passports across

00:01:19.160 --> 00:01:22.020
like he has absolutely nothing to worry about

00:01:22.320 --> 00:01:24.600
the boy pulls out his photo

00:01:24.600 --> 00:01:26.440
black hair gray eyes

00:01:26.440 --> 00:01:28.980
no beard he looks at the man

00:01:29.120 --> 00:01:30.900
he looks back at the photo

00:01:31.120 --> 00:01:34.140
not even close he waves him through

00:01:34.800 --> 00:01:38.100
the scanner agrees green light cleared

00:01:38.800 --> 00:01:41.900
but away from the cameras and the crowds

00:01:42.240 --> 00:01:44.760
the man slips into a quiet hallway

00:01:44.760 --> 00:01:48.320
he peels the beard off also wig away

00:01:48.320 --> 00:01:51.220
pops the contacts out one at a time

00:01:51.400 --> 00:01:53.880
and there he is black hair

00:01:53.880 --> 00:01:56.020
grey eyes no beard

00:01:56.560 --> 00:01:59.600
the face from the poster he was never gone

00:01:59.600 --> 00:02:02.100
he was right there the entire time

00:02:02.200 --> 00:02:03.880
underneath a beard awake

00:02:03.880 --> 00:02:07.240
a different eye color this cannon looked for a face

00:02:07.240 --> 00:02:08.380
it's recognized

00:02:08.400 --> 00:02:11.540
it forms its danger and it waved him through

00:02:11.800 --> 00:02:14.720
this is exactly what polymorphic malware does

00:02:14.720 --> 00:02:17.480
the dangerous code inside never changes

00:02:17.480 --> 00:02:20.760
not a single line but every time it shows up

00:02:20.760 --> 00:02:22.780
it wears a different disguise

00:02:22.880 --> 00:02:25.640
different encryption different packaging

00:02:25.640 --> 00:02:27.600
just different enough to look like something

00:02:27.600 --> 00:02:29.580
the scanner has never seen before

00:02:30.760 --> 00:02:33.740
later that day a woman goins the line

00:02:33.760 --> 00:02:36.660
blonde hair, cut short, slim

00:02:36.920 --> 00:02:39.660
the second interence checks his photo

00:02:39.880 --> 00:02:42.380
brown curly hair and a fuller face

00:02:42.600 --> 00:02:45.940
he looks at her he looks back at the photo

00:02:46.040 --> 00:02:48.060
green light cleared

00:02:48.640 --> 00:02:51.800
she walks through without a word but with a smile

00:02:51.800 --> 00:02:53.380
someone who didn't worry

00:02:53.440 --> 00:02:56.620
because she knew there was never anything to find

00:02:57.200 --> 00:02:59.680
the woman in that photo no longer exist

00:02:59.680 --> 00:03:01.660
not hiding but gone

00:03:01.920 --> 00:03:05.220
this is not a disguise it is a transformation

00:03:06.040 --> 00:03:07.520
a surgeon's office

00:03:07.520 --> 00:03:10.560
a quiet conversation about bone structure

00:03:10.560 --> 00:03:14.220
and what can be changed a gym before sunrise

00:03:14.480 --> 00:03:18.140
month of it the body in that file gone

00:03:18.680 --> 00:03:22.900
a salon chair long brown curls dropping to the floor

00:03:23.320 --> 00:03:25.580
colour pulled out and replaced

00:03:25.680 --> 00:03:28.880
session by session until the mirror showed someone

00:03:28.880 --> 00:03:30.420
the file had never seen

00:03:31.080 --> 00:03:32.980
she did not cover herself up

00:03:33.080 --> 00:03:36.140
she rerolled herself from the inside out

00:03:36.320 --> 00:03:38.620
this is what metamorphic malware does

00:03:38.840 --> 00:03:41.060
it does not change its packaging

00:03:41.080 --> 00:03:44.840
it rewrites its own code the actual instructions

00:03:44.840 --> 00:03:48.660
the logic the structure every single time it runs

00:03:49.000 --> 00:03:51.400
by the time it reaches the next scanner

00:03:51.400 --> 00:03:53.740
that looks nothing like what came before

00:03:54.000 --> 00:03:56.720
the scanner searches for something familiar

00:03:56.720 --> 00:03:58.940
there's nothing familiar to find

00:03:59.200 --> 00:04:03.080
the interns stand quietly in front of their supervisor

00:04:03.080 --> 00:04:06.740
all suspects cleared the gate he already knows

00:04:06.960 --> 00:04:09.500
he lets the silence sit for a moment

00:04:09.560 --> 00:04:11.300
then he leans forward

00:04:11.400 --> 00:04:16.340
one masked, one transformed, one changed his disguise

00:04:16.840 --> 00:04:20.420
one changed herself both fool the scanner

00:04:20.840 --> 00:04:23.100
polymorphic, metamorphic

00:04:23.280 --> 00:04:26.900
when appearance cannot be trusted watch the behavior

